dc_description_s: Oriented with toward the upper right. Map is very similar to "Plan of Detroit" from "Vol. VI, P.L., No. 900", reproduced by Historic Urban Plans. MiU copy has different compass arrow, type used for title and street names, scale bar and lists no publisher. 1 map; 26 x 21 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
